Police are investigating the death of a man who was allegedly killed in a mob justice attack in Kraaifontein. CAPE TOWN - Police are investigating the death of a man who was allegedly killed in a mob justice attack in Kraaifontein.His body was discovered near a train station on Wednesday night with multiple injuries.Locals on a community safety Facebook page claim the man tried to rob a woman on Wednesday night at the Kraaifontein train station.The police s Noloyiso Rwexana says: I can confirm that we re investigating a case of murder after an incident occurred at a railway station in Kraaifontein. According to information, police attended to a complaint at the address and found the body of a 28-year-old man lying on the ground. (Edited by Zamangwane Shange)